App Name helps you find the right service professionals for activities important to you. Whether you are looking to decorate your home, get candid pictures of your wedding, plan your kid’s birthday or get healthier, we are a sure shot destination for your service needs. Our vision is to use technology and smart processes to structure the highly unorganized services market in India. App Name aspires to make hiring a service professional as easy and straightforward as Amazon or Flipkart have made buying products.
